<h2><a href="article.html">Am I just playing games?</a></h2>
<p>The question of &#8220;simply playing games&#8221; in session has emerged repeatedly in my conversations with clinicians. I&#8217;ve had many fruitful discussions about the actual, underlying purpose of bringing games into the therapeutic space. I wanted to consolidate some of those ideas and share them more broadly here, because it is time to put some of that self-doubt to rest.</p>
</article>

